9/18（五） 專題討論（工四講堂）演講題目公告,93,"本週邀請到高雄大學圖書資訊中心主任、資訊管理學系楊新章教授前來演講。講題與摘要如下：
Title: Information Technology on Open Data
Abstract
The publication and utilization of open government data, or open data, have received much attention since the Freedom of Government Information Law comes into force. In fact, the necessity of open data has been widely recognized in last few years and many governments established their open data sites for public use. However, the regulations and publications of open data are still immature since it got popular only in recent years. In this talk, I will give a brief overview on open data from various perspectives. I will also address some issues on applying information technology on open data.
