Important -- ARC renew process,93,"Dear Current Students, Please make sure your ARC's expiration date.
The immigration officers are coming to NDHU on September 10.
You should make the effort to participate the process at that time.
1. To prove your student status in order to renew you ARC, is to pay the tuition fee and get the Register Sticker (from the department) on your student ID card.
2. In case, your ARC needs to be renewed before that, please contact me first. You still need to pay the tuition fee first, then get the ""In School Status Certificate"" from me.
3. All students' ARC only can be renewed at the same area of school (NDHU => Hualien). The immigration office does not allow to renew the ARC in different region (for example, NDHU student does not allow to renew his/her ARC in Taipei).
4. If you must delay the renew process, there is the penalty. Overdue 1~10 days will be charged $2000NT. Overdue 11~20 will be more ...
Please be aware
Dept of CSIE
",Important -- ARC renew process,08/27/2015 - 11:03,/csieweb/zh-tw/node/1859,1859,English
