""Best Of Taiwan's Universities!"" (Newsweek 2014) 
全文：
 http://www.newsweek.com/best-asia-and-south-pacifics-universities/profiles#280153 
簡介：
National Dong Hwa University is reported one of the best universities in Taiwan on Newsweek, a staple of American media for over 80 years, bringing high-quality journalism to millions of readers around the globe.
""As a knowledge provider, National Dong Hwa University offers the most liberal environment, green campus and innovation centers for everyone who wishes to join. With interdisciplinary courses and flexible course taking system, students are encouraged to explore their possibilities outside their comfort zone.
University houses a wide range of research centers ultimately catering to a student body of over ten thousands from 36 different countries. Interactions with the prestigious faculties, multicultural students inspire the Universities to transform into a global recognized institution...""    
