Important Announcement about the 2015 Spring Tuition & Fee Payment,93,"Dear Current Students,
It is your responsibility to PAY OFF all your Tuition and Fee Balance and to UPDATE the On-Line Registration Process before the Registration Day.   
According to NDHU’s Spring 2015 Academic Calendar, the Spring Semester of 2015 starts on 2/24 (Tuesday).
The tuition/fee payment and On-Line Registration Process must finish by 2/26 (Thursday).
The school will not mail copies of payment sheets to you. The Payment sheet for Tuition and Fees can be printed at  Taiwan Bank Student Payment System (https://school.bot.com.tw/twbank.net/index.aspx?pgid=3) .  Use your ARC number for 1st field, Student ID number for 2nd field. The 3rd field is optional. If you still have question, please let us know.   
If you have special circumstance (for example: cannot pay on time, not back to Taiwan yet, waiting for scholarship process …etc.), you should apply a written “Postpone Request ( get the form here )  ” to school and submit it to the CSIE Department Office ASAP, no later than 2/26. The written postpone request will be reviewed by the Department Chairman and the School Officers.  There is NO guarantee on the result of the request. If the request is granted, the latest payment due day may be extended to 3/12. (as 14 working days after the Registration Day). 
If the circumstance is extraordinary, you should make a written request of the “Installment Payment Plan ( get the form here ) ” to school and submit it to the CSIE Department Office ASAP, no later than 2/26. The written postpone request will be reviewed by the Department Chair and School Officers. There is NO guarantee on the result of the request. If the request is granted, the latest payment due day may be extended to 6/16 (as 1 week prior to the final exam and the last day of withdrawing the semester). 

All students, including both ""postpone"" and ""installment"" students,  MUST PAY  Dormitory Fee & Room Deposit, Student Group Insurance Fee, and Taiwan National Health Insurance Fee (NHI) by 3/12.  No exception! 
If you do not pay on-time as promised in Installment Payment Plan, or do not PAY OFF all your Tuition and Fee Balance by the last day, you WILL be expelled from NDHU, and the result will affect your future study. 

Postpone Request / Installment Payment Plan Request (both Chinese & English) 學雜費延緩 / 分期繳交申請書 :
 http://www.aa.ndhu.edu.tw/files/14-1006-58085,r1067-1.php 
 
NDHU’s Spring 2015 Academic Calendar (in English) : 
 http://www.aa.ndhu.edu.tw/ezfiles/6/1006/img/946/103calendar_en.pdf   
Guideline of handling the delayed payment (in English) 延誤繳交學雜費之處理原則 : 
 http://www.aa.ndhu.edu.tw/files/14-1006-24226,r1064-1.php 
NDHU 2014 Student Group Insurance Guideline 103學年度學生團體保險須知 : 
 http://www.student.ndhu.edu.tw/ezfiles/7/1007/attach/2/pta_35217_5008490_74561.pdf 
NDHU Academic Regulation (in English) 東華大學學則 : 
 http://www.aa.ndhu.edu.tw/files/14-1006-43648,r1065-1.php 
Dept of CSIE
