【TEDｘNDHU：12/26 See Different World】by Sven Riemenschneider、張爾康、and Prof. Jason Grenier ,93,"【TEDｘNDHU：12/26 See Different World】
This is part of TEDxNDHU lecture series [See the world in a different perspective]. In Taiwan, we often receive a variety of influences, but lack of a broad view of the world.  We hope through this lecture seris to give the audience a chance to see a different world; allowing us to think how to change our perspective of looking at the world, and being more diverses and riches to re-examine the society we live in. 
TEDxNDHU will invite speakers from different countries, cultures, subjects from their own experiences and observations to share.   More Information: https://www.facebook.com/pages/TEDx-NDHU/625838434195042?ref=hl
Speakers：Prof. Jason Grenier, CSIE Exchange's 張爾康, CSIE Bacheloar's Sven Riemenschneider
