2014 Fall Semester Transferring Procedure ,93,"2014 Fall Semester Transferring Procedure and Application Submission
Application Submission: July 9 - July 18, 2014.
1st Departmental Review Result by July 30
2nd Departmental Review Result by August 7 (for 2nd choice application) 
All students must meet requirements, prepare early, and submit application timely. All application are reviewed by Departmental Committee.
Transferring Application and Regulation can be downloaded here:
 http://www.aa.ndhu.edu.tw/files/14-1006-57167,r1064-1.php  
Frequently Asked Questions Q & A:
Q: What if I am not in school during the summer, and 2014-Spring class scores are not ready, how can I apply?
A: Student may make special advanced request (""證明文件申請單"") to request one’s Transcript.  When the scores are ready, Office of the Academic Affair will print out your transcript and deliver to the Department for you.
",2014 Fall Semester Transferring Procedure ,07/09/2014 - 12:19,/csieweb/zh-tw/node/1472,1472,English
103學年度第1學期轉系所申請公告,93,"摘錄103學年度第1學期轉系、所申請、審核作業時程如下：
學生遞交申請書：103年7月9日~7月18日
第一批系所審查截止日(第一志願通過、未通過且無第二志願者)：7月30日
第二批系所審查截止日(第一志願未通過送交第二志願系所者)：8月7日
請同學配合規定、及早準備，並按時程繳交。轉系申請審核需經系務會議決議。
轉系所申請表請至教務處網頁→下載專區→表單下載→103學年度第1學期學生轉系所申請表下載(連結已失效)

常見問題Q&A：
Q：因102-2成績未到齊，故期末印出的成績單未完整，但因為暑假期間不在學校該如何申請？
A:學生可先至註冊組填寫證明文件申請單申請成績單，待成績到齊後，由註冊組列印代交至系所。
