6/13(五)Seminar演講通知--Fault Detection of Wireless Sensor Networks,92,"演講通知
【主 講 人】林政寬 教授 蘇州大學 計算機學院
【時      間】103年6月13日(五) 14：00 ~ 16：00
【地      點】工四講堂
【題      目】Fault Detection of Wireless Sensor Networks
  Abstract
  Wireless sensor network (WSN) has attracted a lot of attention. Recently, research efforts have been dedicated to power management, routing, deployment and coverage, and localization. Applications of WSNs include habitat monitoring, wildfire monitoring, healthcare system, and emergency navigation. In WSN, the harsh environment makes sensor nodes into fault are common. To ensure the QoS of WSN, it need to be able to detect the faults. Existing diagnosis schemes in wireless sensor networks are generally sink-based, which collects information from all sensor nodes so as to conduct centralized analysis. The sink-based diagnosis tools incur huge communication overhead to the traffic sensitive sensor networks. Moreover, the unreliable wireless communications make that the sink obtains incomplete or suspicious information. To address the above issues, we present a distributed diagnosis algorithm. Each sensor can self-diagnosis by comparing its current sensing data with its neighbors. Finally, it outputs the final diagnosis report.
",6/13(五)Seminar演講通知--Fault Detection of Wireless Sensor Networks,06/11/2014 - 17:04,/csieweb/zh-tw/node/1488,1488,"Chinese, Traditional"
