"Seminar演講通知-4/18(五)Researches for Low-Power, High Performance Embedded Multi-core Video Decoder",92,"【主 講 人】鍾崇斌 教授 國立交通大學資訊工程學系
【時	  間】103年4月18日(五)  14：00 ~ 16：00
【地	  點】工四講堂
【題   目】Researches for Low-Power, High Performance Embedded Multi-core Video Decoder
Abstract:
   Hot applications on embedded systems include web surfing, internet chatting, social networking, video playback, and gaming. And video playback has become one of the most important functions of modern embedded systems like smart phones, tablets, and TV set-top boxes. We study two critical topics in video playback:
1. Exploiting parallelism in H.264 deblocking filtering by operation reordering; and
2. Reducing decoder’s Decoded Picture Buffer size by keeping only useful pixels when the frames are no longer highly utilized.
   Multifaceted goals are to be achieved: High performance, low power consumption, and low hardware cost.  We achieve these goals via exploiting parallelism and reducing memory needs.
