Congratulations! CSIE is the champion of the Excellent Website Competition!,164,"CSIE website stood out form 43 Departments in the College of Science and Enginnering, Management, Humanities and Social Science, Indigenous Studies, Marine Sciences, Education as well as The Arts, 
and won Section 102 NDHU first semester Excellent Website Competition : Chinese version and English version DOUBLE championship.
Moreover, the website recieved some good comments.
 
Chinese Version： advantage
1.Have all the qualities of Good Website：
(1)Good visual sense.
(2Good website framework and classification of imformation.
(3)Easy to read the website's content.
(4)Browsing smoothly
(5)Sufficient information
(6)Good maintenance
2.Recommend:
(1)Classify the bulletin with Class as sublist in order to query.
(2)Website browse counter has a characteristic.
3.Artistic quality：
(1)Cool calm style, especially the hue and page switching of banner, is a xcellent design and the website has a good sence of design.
(2)The clear layout and good color scheme are benefit for the user to browse.
(3)The sytle and coler scheme of this website are consistent. The framework and content are clear. Therefore, this website is eazy to read for the user.
 
English Version : Advantage 
1.The website has been updating all the time such as provide the newest news.
2.The outline of website is very clear. The classification of every section is clear. 
3.The website using the simple English. The international student can easily understand the content of the website
 
