Congratulations!  Our 1st Graduated Student from International Master Program - Yudy,93," CSIE International Master Student--  Yudy from Indonesia , started the program in the Spring of 2011. 
Overcame the language barriers, concentrated on academic works, actively integrated into the campus life, and initiatively helped new students to adapt the environment. Yudy maintained  a straight A+, GPA 4.50, for two consecutive semesters,  in result of receiving ""NDHU's Outstanding Scholar Honor Award"". In the Summer of 2012, he actively seeked the opportunities to participate in the study plan of Academia Sinica and had a three-month internship experience. In the end of January of 2013, Yudy successfully completed the thesis and passed the defense.  He became the first graduated student from International Master Program of Department of Computer Science & Information Engineer (CSIE), NDHU.
In a very short period of time, Yudy received a job offer, and would start to work in HsinChu Science Park soon.  
Sincerely Congradulations and Best Wishes from the faculty and the classmates of Department of CSIE!! 

Yudy 畢業感言： 
In past two years, I have studied many new things in Dong Hwa University. This makes me can get job in Taiwan even though my Chinese language isn’t that good.  Now I am working in Hsinchu Science Park, the biggest industry area in Taiwan.  
I appreciate very much for Dong Hwa has given me, especially from the Department of Computer Science & Information Engineering, Office of International Affairs, and many staffs. I miss the environment of NDHU and friends in Hualien.  
Wish more international students to come.   Sincerely, Thank You!
Yudy 2013.03.02
",Congratulations!  Our 1st Graduated Student from International Master Program - Yudy,04/01/2013 - 23:09,/csieweb/zh-tw/node/940,940,English
恭喜 ! 本系國際碩士班第一位畢業生-- Yudy,93," 本系國際班碩士生Yudy (陳春瑞，來自印尼)，於 99-2 入學。在學期間克服語言障礙，努力學業，踴躍融入東華生活，主動協助新生適應環境。 連續二學期保持著全A+，GPA 4.50的好成績，獲得東華書卷獎。101年暑假積極爭取參與中研院學習計畫，並且得到3個月的實習機會。Yudy在102年1月底順利完成論文並通過口試，成為本系國際碩士班第一位畢業生。  
在非常短的時間內，Yudy 馬上獲得機會，即將在新竹科學園區上班。全系師生在此祝福他一帆風順!!

Yudy 畢業感言： 
In past two years, I have studied many new things in Dong Hwa University. This makes me can get job in Taiwan even though my Chinese language isn’t that good.  Now I am working in Hsinchu Science Park, the biggest industry area in Taiwan.  
I appreciate very much for Dong Hwa has given me, especially from the Department of Computer Science & Information Engineering, Office of International Affairs, and many staffs. I miss the environment of NDHU and friends in Hualien.  
Wish more international students to come.   Sincerely, Thank You!
Yudy 2013.03.02
