",基本程式能力檢定於2012.10.24 (三)晚上7時在工B305電腦教室登場 (有照片),10/30/2012 - 10:57,/csieweb/zh-tw/node/659,659,"Chinese, Traditional"
11/2(五)Seminar演講通知,92," 適用類別 ： 系所師生
 演講題目 ： 建構於智慧型手機與無線感測器網路之運動行為偵測系統
 演講者 ： 慈濟大學醫學資訊系教授 潘健一教授
 演講日期 ： 2012-11-02
 演講時間 ： 14:00-16:00
 演講地點 ： 3F工四講堂
 內容 ： 摘要:Recently, exercise is recognized as one effective clinical prescription that can achieve conspicuous improvements on chronic patients healthy. However, to most patients, the compliance of exercise prescription is the worst performance rather than others prescriptions. One of the challenges faced by physicians and patients is lack of effective and self-administrated approach to tracking and recording the patients exercise behavior in a period of time. In this research, we present an exercise activity detection system that based on sensor network and smart personal device technology. First, the patient activities are captured by one, or up to two, tri-axis accelerometer-based sensors. Next, the body movement information is transfer to smart phone for further exercise activities classification. The sensors and smart phone form a sensor network that base on the Piconet in Bluetooth wireless technology. Then, the exercise type and duration time can be recognized and recorded in the patient’s smart phone. The detected exercise behavior from the proposed system can provide physicians to real know the compliance situation of that patient. On the other hand, the proposed system can also facilitate the self-administrated approach for patients to improving their healthy. 
",11/2(五)Seminar演講通知,10/30/2012 - 10:14,/csieweb/zh-tw/node/658,658,"Chinese, Traditional"
10/26 Seminar 演講公告，講題為A Group Profile based Dynamic Program Recommander on P2P-IPTV,92,"適用類別 ： 系所師生
 演講題目 ： A Group Profile based Dynamic Program Recommander on P2P-IPTV
 演講者 ： 國立台灣科技大學電機工程系教授 陳建中教授
 演講日期 ： 2012-10-26
 演講時間 ： 14:00-16:00
 演講地點 ： 3F工四講堂
內容 ： Abstract: Though the IPTV (Internet Protocal TV) market and applications are expected to flourish, to make profits under this high investments and competitive environment, the efficiency of an IPTV program recommender becomes the dominant factor. The recommender system has been widely used in E-commerce and has become one standard basic function. It not only can increase the cross-selling rate, but also increase the customer loyalty, due to its satisfactory recommendation. The recommendation methods in general can be classified into content-based recommendation (CR) and collaborative filter (CF) approaches. The former suffers limited recommendation scope, while the latter suffers the so-called cold-start problem. A hybrid approach that utilized the advantages of both CR and CF has been proposed to improve the recommendation efficiency. Though efficient, the recommendation methods are limited to server single user at one time. It’s just the time to develop recommendation method based on group profile, since the IPTV would soon become our everyday life. To make group profile recommendation feasible, we proposed to design contactless natural human-machine interface. This human oriented interface would help to promote the group profile recommendation system. It can also record and learn user preference to improve the recommendation accuracy. The group profile based program recommender based on IPTV would provide a total solution to make the whole system feasible. 
",10/26 Seminar 演講公告，講題為A Group Profile based Dynamic Program Recommander on P2P-IPTV,10/23/2012 - 11:29,/csieweb/zh-tw/node/657,657,"Chinese, Traditional"
