CSIE Rule of the Primary Programming Proficiency (PPP) Certification 2012.10.03,93," 
The Latest Rule of PPP Certification had been updated to http://english.csie.ndhu.edu.tw/csieweb/en/node/1783 (2013.11.27)
 PDF Print Version
Rule of the Primary Programming Proficiency (PPP) Certification for
Department of Computer Science & Information Engineering 
National Dong Hwa Universality
基本程式能力檢定辦法
 
Approved by the Departmental Committee of Curriculum Designing and Planning on 2012.09.06
                                                                                                                                        Approved by the Departmental Executive Committee on 2012.10.03
 
The PPP certification aims to ensure that the students in the Department of Computer Science & Information Engineering (CSIE) have developed qualified primary programming proficiency for software design before they can graduate from the department. This rule is made to regulate the enforcement of the PPP certification.   
This rule applies to all undergraduate students (including the International Bachelor classes) admitted in/after the 2012 School Year (2012 Fall).
Before graduation, each student is required to receive the PPP certification by passing an on-site and real-time programming test held in the department each semester. The scope of the programming test would cover comprehensively the programming skills trained in the core courses including Introduction to Computer Programming (I) + (II) and Data Structures.
For each student, there is no upper limit on the number of tests he/she can attend during his/her studying in the department.
Students who want to participate in a test must register to the department office within 2 weeks after each semester begins. The date to perform the test will be announced on the departmental website before the registration procedure starts.  
The test duration is 3 hours. Each participant is required to solve at least 3 programming problems to pass the test. The names of all participants passing the test will be announced on the departmental website.
By fulfilling the following conditions, along with the submission of official carnets, is considered to be equivalent to the PPP certification:Receiving programming-related certificates approved by the PPP Certification Committee of the department;
Participating in National Collegiate Programming Contest (NCPC) organized by Taiwan’s Minister Of Education (教育部舉辦全國大專電腦軟體設計競賽), ACM International Collegiate Programming Contest (ACM國際大學程式競賽), or other programming contests approved by the PPP Certification Committee, and receiving an award credited as “Excellent Work” or better.
Participating the Collegiate Programming Examination (大學程式能力檢定), and receiving a test score falling within the top 50% in that examination.

This rule has been established by Departmental Committee of Curriculum Designing and Planning,  approved by Departmental Executive Meeting, and announced publically afterwards. The same procedure should be proceeded for future modifications.
 
PDF Print Version
",CSIE Rule of the Primary Programming Proficiency (PPP) Certification 2012.10.03,09/24/2012 - 10:22,/csieweb/zh-tw/node/631,631,English
國立東華大學資訊工程學系基本程式能力檢定辦法 2012.10.03,93,"國立東華大學資訊工程學系基本程式能力檢定辦法
註：已經有更新版--國立東華大學資訊工程學系基本程式能力畢業標準實施辦法 2013.11.27   http://www.csie.ndhu.edu.tw/csieweb/zh-tw/node/1646 
101年9 月 6日課程暨學程規劃委員會議通過
101年10月 3日系務會議通過
依101年 10 月 3 日系務會議決議，自101學年度起入學之學士班(含國際學士班)學生開始適用
第一條	國立東華大學資訊工程學系（以下簡稱本系）為加強學生程式設計能力，並提昇軟體開發與專案製作之執行力，特訂定「基本程式能力檢定辦法」（以下簡稱檢定考）。
第二條	本檢定考適用對象為本系101學年度以後入學之學士班(含國際學士班)學生。
第三條	檢定考以程式設計(一)、程式設計(二)及資料結構所教授內容為範圍，考試以上機實作方式進行。
第四條	學生參加本檢定考沒有次數上之限制，可重覆參加至通過為止。
第五條	同學於電腦教室實作程式，測驗結果將公佈於本系網頁，檢定時程為每學期開學後2周內報名，報名截止後一個月內施測，學生參加應試前必須先報名。
第六條	學生應考成績以答對3題為通過，施測時間為三小時。
第七條	本系學生符合下列條件者，得檢附相關證明文件，經本系程式能力檢定委員會通過者，視同通過本檢定考。
   (1)	取得本系核可之程式設計相關證照。
   (2)	參加教育部舉辦全國大專電腦軟體設計競賽、 ACM國際大學程式競賽或本系核可之程式競賽，成績在佳作以上。
   (3)	參加Collegiate Programming Examination(大學程式能力檢定)，成績在當次測驗中排名前50%者。
第八條	本辦法由課程暨學程規劃委員會擬定，經系務會議通過後公告實施，修正時亦同。
