Regulation of CSIE Graduate Student Scholarship as 970305,93,"Regulation of CSIE Graduate Student Scholarship as 970305
一、 This Regulation is based on the Regulation of NDHU Graduate Student Scholarship, specially supported by Ministry of Education, Taiwan, R.O.C.二、 The maxinum length of CSIE Graduate Student Scholarship for Master Students is 2 School Years, for Ph.D. Students is 3 School Years.三、 The distribution of this scholarship is ordered as below:1. Ph.D. Students, $8,000 NT per school month for 1st thru 3rd year of study;2. Master Students, $5,000 NT per school month for 1st year of study;3. If there is any money amount left, the money will be divided into the remaining of the qualified graduate students (1st thru 2nd year of Master students);四、 All qualified students must sign the Scholarship Declaration form each semester.   See the department office for the latest form.
 
 
