International Undergraduate - Recruitment Information,1," For International Students

All MUST Read  The Advantages of Studying in Dept of CSIE at NDHU 
Program Types:
　● 1-year Chinese Language plus 4-year Chinese-Taught Computer Science & Information Engineering Bachelor Program. 
　　　(total 5-year scholarship program sponsored by Taiwan ICDF Scholarship)
　● 4-year Chinese-Taught Computer Science & Information Engineering Bachelor Program
　● 4-year English-Taught Computer Science & Information Engineering Bachelor Program  

Application Submission:
　　　 From December 1 2014 to March 31 2015.  Check Application Forms Here...  OR  On-line Application... . 
School Year
　　　Fall Semester: September ~ January
　　　Spring Semester: February ~ June
Required Documents:
　　　1. Admission/Scholarship Application Form
　　　2. Verification of Nationality
　　　3. Diploma of the High School or equivalent degree(issued or translated in English)
　　　4. The original transcripts of the High School or equivalent degree (issued or translated in English)
　　　5. Certificate of Language Proficiency
　　　6. Autobiography
　　　7. Study Plan
　　　8. Two Letters of Recommendation
　　　9. Any supplemental documents (such as Awards, Certifications, Exams, Volunteers, ...etc.) to enhance yourself
Application Forms can be downloaded at NDHU Office of International Affairs / International Students OR Apply On-line. 

We are NDHU。CSIE


