International Undergraduate - Admission Procedure,1,"According to the School Calendar for all Admission Procedures

2014~2015 School Calendar (English)
Prospective Students 
NDHU Office of International Affair (OIA) 
NDHU Campus Map (English)
Transportation between NDHU campus and Downtown Hualien City 

School Calendar at Glance 

08/22 ~ 9/19 -- pay period for Tuition, Association Fees, Dorm Insurance ...etc.
09/09 ~ 9/11 -- Arrive to Taiwan 
09/10 ~ 9/11 -- Dorm move-in / Registration for New International Students
September 12 -- International Student Orientation 
09/13 ~ 9/16 -- NDHU Entire Campus 4-day Freshmen Orientation / Get to know your department
September 17 -- Begin Day of 2014 Fall Semester
September 19 -- End of Registration Day and Payment Due for 2014 Fall Semester
09/17 ~ 9/22 -- On-Line Course Selection for NEW Students
09/24 ~ 9/30 -- On-Line Course Selection for OLD Students
10/03 ~ 10/9 -- Manual Add/Drop Course Requests
October 10　  -- Double Tenth, National Day (Holiday, no class)
11/10 ~ 11/14 -- Mid-Term Exam Week 
11/10 ~ 12/05 -- Course Withdrawal Period
11/18 ~ 11/19 -- NDHU Anniversary & NDHU International Day 
12/22 ~ 01/02 -- On-Line Course Selection for next semester
January 6  　　-- Last Day to withdraw entire semester (no record of learning) 
01/12 ~ 01/16 -- Final Exam Week
January 19 　 -- Begin Day of Winter Vacation
January 21 　 -- Move-Out Day of Dormitory / Winter Dorm Relocation 



 2/18 ~ 2/23 -- Chinese Lunar New Year 
 February 23 -- Move-In Day of Dormitory
  
 February 24 -- Begin Day of 2015 Spring Semester
 2/25 ~ 2/26 -- Registration Day, Pay Tuition, Dorm, Insurance, Fees... etc. 
 February 26 -- International Student Orientation for NEW Master/Doctor Students
  
 2/27 ~ 2/28 -- 228 Memorial Day – Holiday
 3/02 ~ 3/06 -- On-line Add/Drop Courses
 3/10 ~ 3/16 -- Manual Add/Drop Courses
 4/02 ~ 4/06 -- Spring Break - Holiday
 4/20 ~ 4/24 -- Midterm Exams Week
 4/20 ~ 5/15 -- Course Withdrawal Period
 6/02 ~ 6/13 -- Course Preliminary Selection For Next Semester
 June 13　　-- Graduation Ceremony (Commencement)
 June 16　　-- Last Day to withdraw entire semester (no record of learning) 
 6/19 ~ 6/20 -- Dragon Boat Festival - Holiday
 6/22 ~ 6/26 -- Final Exams Week
 June 29　　-- Begin Day of Summer Vacation
 July 01　　 -- Move-Out Day of Dormitory / Summer Dorm Relocation 


