Undergraduate,1,"Undergraduate Program
The general 4-year undergraduate program is meant for all Chinese speaking students. (e.g. Taiwanese Students, Oversea Chinese Students, Oversea Born Chinese...etc.).
The Department of CSIE offers   All English Taught International Undergraduate Program .  Please check our  International Undergraduate Webpage  for detail.  
